Description:
It Feels like a House!
You won’t believe it until you see it, but this renovated unit really feels more like a house. The space, the design, the finishes and features – you are going to love every bit of it! Cathedral ceilings for a bit of extra room, a neat and tidy kitchen with breakfast bench that flows into the meals area, three bedrooms all with built in robes, a private covered deck area and a terrace to unwind on after a long day – this is heavenly. Features include the double lock up garage, two split system units and ducted heating. It’s also within walking distance to, the Plaza, public transport, the local shops at Autumn Place and easy access to Monash Freeway, Eastlink, Princes Highway and South Gippsland Highway. This well positioned home offers both convenience and easy access to local amenities. You don’t want to miss out on this gem!
There’s so much to love about this home. On entry the ceiling of the living add class and style to such a premium home and it flows freely into the meals area and kitchen. Each of the bedrooms are a good size and the master has access to the central contemporary bathroom and ther are also security roller blinds. Plus if you love to entertain, head to the rear and celebrate any occasion on the sun soaked deck! Or relax and have a snooze in another amazing private rear covered entertaining area with decking and extra yard space for the kids to play!
This is a prime opportunity for young families, first home buyers, investors and even downsizers. With a location like this you can so close to schools like Dandenong Primary, St John’s College, St Mary’s and the kindergarten is close too. Plus the ever thriving hub of Dandenong Central is a mere moment away where you have shops, buses, trains, cafes and restaurants.
For quality, comfort and class, you need to take a look at this superb home!

Description:
THE BEST IN EASY CARE AND CONVENIENT DANDENONG LIVING!
Are you ready to enjoy a low-maintenance and relaxed property that has fantastic quality, terrific space, and a location close to superb Dandenong attractions? If so, you can't ignore this 2 bedroom unit which offers a wonderful opportunity for first home buyers and investors.
This charming single level retreat has easy living in mind. Major highlights include beautiful timber floors through much of the property, spacious central lounge ideal for everyday living, sizeable kitchen and meals with appliances including a dishwasher, both bedrooms with built-in robes, renovated bathroom, laundry, private back garden, ducted heating, air-conditioning, double carport, and visitor parking.
You're in a highly convenient location close to Dandenong Plaza Shopping Centre, Dandenong West Primary School, Dandenong High School, Greaves Reserve, John Hemmings Memorial Park, buses, Eastlink, and Dandenong Station.

Description:
A Metro Village Beauty!
This modern and immaculately presented property is sure to appeal to all first home buyers and investors. Situated in Dandenong’s newest estate Metro Village, you will feel as though everything is literally at your doorstep with Dandenong Railway Station a short walk away, the Eastlink Freeway just minutes up the road and all of central Dandenong’s amenities including Market, Plaza and Hospital around the corner from this home. Facing towards beautiful parklands, the stunning 2 bedroom home offers an impressive open living, meals and kitchen area, master bedroom with balcony and corner windows that provide amazing views, modern central bathroom, concealed European laundry, kitchen incorporating 900mm stainless steel gas cook top, brand new oven, dishwasher and pantry and central gas ducted heating and split system air conditioning. You will also absolutely love the outdoor spaces that this home provides with a magnificent veranda looking towards the Dandenong CBD and a huge patio that is sure to provide a perfect setting for summer barbeques with family and friends. With 2 secure car spaces including a single lock up garage with remote access and single carport as well as loads of external storage and impressive gardens all round, this home is a little gem. Make a time to inspect it now as properties of this calibre and in this area sell very quickly.
Contact: Neb Delibasic on 0411 332 467

Description:
Picture Perfect!
A wonderful opportunity to purchase a unique two storey family home in one of Dandenong's most sought after locations. This magnificent family residence is an architectural triumph of superior design and remarkable quality, offering the ultimate in family living and entertaining comprising of 6 spacious bedrooms (4 bedrooms located downstairs, 2 located upstairs) & 2 bathrooms. With flawless indoor design you will appreciate the open plan kitchen with stainless steel appliances, gas cooking and electric oven plus an abundance of space for the whole family with 3 large living areas.
The second level is a self-contained area with a bonus kitchen. Enjoy the comforts in the house of ducted heating and split system air-conditioning. You will also appreciate the separate studio with built in bar plus a fantastic large outdoor decked BBQ/entertaining area.
Conveniently located near Dandenong North Primary School, Dandenong High School, Emerson School, St Gerard's Primary School, Chisholm Institute TAFE, Dandenong Hospital and JC Mills Reserve as well as the vibrant Dandenong Markets and Dandenong Plaza. Also close to the Dandenong Train Station, nearby bus transportation and easy access to both Eastlink and the Monash Freeway.
It's not every day that you come across a versatile home like this where your dreams can be turned into reality.

We do not accept any responsibility to any person for its accuracy and do no more than pass it on. Description:
Contemporary Living in Enviable Locale
Sale By SET DATE: Tuesday 5th June at 5pm (unless sold prior)
This beautifully presented modern apartment cannot be beat on location. Being Central Dandenong and a short walk to the Dandenong Station and all other amenities that you would ever need - this is ideal for first home buyers and investors alike.
The apartment is comprised of 1 large bedroom with built in robes, separate toilet and bathroom with extra laundry space and an inverter split system for heating and cooling. It boasts contemporary kitchen with stainless steel appliance including Dishwasher, plenty of storage space and an expansive dining and living area that open out to a spacious, private, balcony for outdoor entertaining and room for a barbeque.
Added features include elevator, secure basement parking with your own individual storage space and intercom entry for added security.
If you are looking for low maintenance, convenience & modern living then look no further. All you have to do is move in – so call now for an inspection!

Description:
CENTRAL COURT LOCATION!
Nestled in a quiet court location yet within a short walk to St Johns College, Dandenong Plaza, Market and many other central amenities is this North-East facing three bedroom home, ideal for the retiree or first home buyer on a budget.
It offers an L shaped lounge/dining off the modern kitchen with gas cooking and plenty of cupboard space. The bedrooms are serviced by an ensuite effect full family bathroom and a separate toilet. The spacious laundry offers access to the tranquil backyard with shady green trees and a garden shed.
Other features include gas heating, gas hot water service, air conditioning, aluminium windows, security doors and a single carport.
*** Freshly painted & new flooring in lounge & dining rooms ***
AFFORDABLE OPPORTUNITY!

Description:
Low maintenance living, Close to all amenities!
This low maintenance home is the ideal start for first home buyers or investors and is also great for people looking to downsize.
Located in Dandenong Central, approximately 1 km from Dandenong Plaza and Dandenong Market, everything you need is within a short walk.
This home offers three spacious bedrooms, large lounge, and large kitchen with meals area. A front verandah overlooks the front garden, whilst a fully fenced, private rear yard offers ample space for kids or pets with access to a single lock up garage.
The home is the front one of only two on the block and is within walking distance to all of Dandenong amenities as well as providing easy access to Princes Hwy and Eastlink.
